title: Westside Gunn drops by the show!
description:
A lot to get to in today's show, including Luka Doncic putting on a show vs KD and Kyrie, Lamar Jackson doing what Lamar Jackson does, and further burying Brady and the Bucs, and previews of Bills-Packers and Lions-Miami... but the star of the show is Westside Gunn, the FLerYGOD. His new album "10" is out now, and it loaded with features: Ghostface and Raekwon, Black Star, Run the Jewels, and all the Griselda stars. Pull up!
